      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_b8b9c4575f1b632a29301bed7edc80c5">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged chronologically.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <bioghist id="aspace_a846287b32eaa8fd17b5b62cd462381c">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Faculty Committee on Athletics is appointed annually by the Yale president. It serves in an advisory capacity to the director of athletics and to the president. The committee meets monthly to discuss issues affecting athletes and athletics at Yale.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_6eb7a26ad2c27a0dcc562069e012e323">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of proceedings of the Yale Faculty Committee on Athletics.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
